item.title: Meow, World!
item.description: My first attempt at writing a blog post.

Priydarshi Singh is a first year undergraduate student at Indian Institute Of Technology, Kanpur, majoring in Aerospace Engineering. His academic interests include cyber security and artificial intelligence. He is a learning developer. For recreation he prefers mind sports like chess, competitive programming or puzzling. He is also an avid quizzer, a swimmer and a budding water-polo player.
